    <title>Hexo</title>
    <link href="/2024/12/16/hexo/"/>
    <url>/2024/12/16/hexo/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo"><a href="#Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Hexo"></a>Hexo</h1><h2 id="一、如何部署环境"><a href="#一、如何部署环境" class="headerlink" title="一、如何部署环境"></a>一、如何部署环境</h2><h3 id="1-安装nodejs"><a href="#1-安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="1.安装nodejs"></a>1.安装nodejs</h3><figure class="highlight 1c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs 1c"><span class="hljs-number">01</span>下载地址：https<span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-comment">//nodejs.org</span><br><span class="hljs-number">02</span>下载长期支持版（LTS）<br><span class="hljs-number">03</span>安装：下一步、下一步<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-打开命令符"><a href="#2-打开命令符" class="headerlink" title="2.打开命令符"></a>2.打开命令符</h3><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crmsh"><span class="hljs-number">01</span>Win+R<br><span class="hljs-number">02</span>输入cmd，Enter<br><span class="hljs-number">03</span>查看<span class="hljs-keyword">node</span><span class="hljs-title">版本：在命令符中输入node</span> -v<br><span class="hljs-number">04</span>查看npm版本：在命令符中输入npm -v<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-全局安装hexo"><a href="#3-全局安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="3.全局安装hexo"></a>3.全局安装hexo</h3><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm">npm install -g hexo-<span class="hljs-keyword">cli</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-验证安装成功"><a href="#4-验证安装成功" class="headerlink" title="4.验证安装成功"></a>4.验证安装成功</h3><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo -v</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-建立一个空文件夹：位置可自选，我这里是选择在E盘"><a href="#5-建立一个空文件夹：位置可自选，我这里是选择在E盘" class="headerlink" title="5.建立一个空文件夹：位置可自选，我这里是选择在E盘"></a>5.建立一个空文件夹：位置可自选，我这里是选择在E盘</h3><figure class="highlight dos"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dos"><span class="hljs-number">01</span>在命令符中输入：e:<br><span class="hljs-number">02</span><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> hexoblog<br>或<br><span class="hljs-built_in">md</span> hexoblog<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-进入文件夹hexoblog"><a href="#6-进入文件夹hexoblog" class="headerlink" title="6.进入文件夹hexoblog"></a>6.进入文件夹hexoblog</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> hexoblog<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="二、如何初始化个人博客"><a href="#二、如何初始化个人博客" class="headerlink" title="二、如何初始化个人博客"></a>二、如何初始化个人博客</h2><h3 id="1-初始化博客"><a href="#1-初始化博客" class="headerlink" title="1.初始化博客"></a>1.初始化博客</h3><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs csharp">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">init</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-启动博客"><a href="#2-启动博客" class="headerlink" title="2.启动博客"></a>2.启动博客</h3><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo s</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-访问博客地址"><a href="#3-访问博客地址" class="headerlink" title="3.访问博客地址"></a>3.访问博客地址</h3><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-symbol">http:</span><span class="hljs-comment">//localhost:4000/</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-断开链接"><a href="#4-断开链接" class="headerlink" title="4.断开链接"></a>4.断开链接</h3><figure class="highlight mathematica"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs mathematica"><span class="hljs-variable">Ctrl</span><span class="hljs-operator">+</span><span class="hljs-built_in">C</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="三、如何写博客"><a href="#三、如何写博客" class="headerlink" title="三、如何写博客"></a>三、如何写博客</h2><h3 id="1-写一篇新的文章"><a href="#1-写一篇新的文章" class="headerlink" title="1.写一篇新的文章"></a>1.写一篇新的文章</h3><figure class="highlight actionscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs actionscript">hexo <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;文章名&quot;</span><br><br>或<br><br>hexo n <span class="hljs-string">&quot;文章名&quot;</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-编辑文献内容"><a href="#2-编辑文献内容" class="headerlink" title="2.编辑文献内容"></a>2.编辑文献内容</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-number">01</span><span class="hljs-string">找到文章所在文章打开</span><br><span class="hljs-number">02</span><span class="hljs-string">编辑</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">### 第一章</span><br><br><span class="hljs-string">内容1</span><br><span class="hljs-string">内容2</span><br><span class="hljs-string">内容3</span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-meta"></span><br><span class="hljs-comment">### 第二章</span><br><br><span class="hljs-string">内容1</span><br><span class="hljs-string">内容2</span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">---</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">### 参考文献</span><br><br><span class="hljs-string">内容1</span><br><span class="hljs-string">内容2</span><br><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs">01基于markdown语法<br>02编辑器可用VSCODE等，可自行选择<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-清理缓存"><a href="#3-清理缓存" class="headerlink" title="3.清理缓存"></a>3.清理缓存</h3><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo clean</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-生成"><a href="#4-生成" class="headerlink" title="4.生成"></a>4.生成</h3><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css">hexo <span class="hljs-selector-tag">g</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-重新启动"><a href="#5-重新启动" class="headerlink" title="5.重新启动"></a>5.重新启动</h3><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo s</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="四、如何把个人博客部署到远端"><a href="#四、如何把个人博客部署到远端" class="headerlink" title="四、如何把个人博客部署到远端"></a>四、如何把个人博客部署到远端</h2><h3 id="1-创建并登录github"><a href="#1-创建并登录github" class="headerlink" title="1.创建并登录github"></a>1.创建并登录github</h3><figure class="highlight 1c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs 1c">网址：https<span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-comment">//github.com/</span><br>如访问较慢，可用https<span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-comment">//github.ur1.fun/加速</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-新建仓库"><a href="#2-新建仓库" class="headerlink" title="2.新建仓库"></a>2.新建仓库</h3><figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs lua"><span class="hljs-number">01</span>仓库命名规则：昵称+github.<span class="hljs-built_in">io</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-安装git插件"><a href="#3-安装git插件" class="headerlink" title="3.安装git插件"></a>3.安装git插件</h3><figure class="highlight ada"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ada">npm install <span class="hljs-comment">--save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-设置hexoblog文件夹下的-config文件"><a href="#4-设置hexoblog文件夹下的-config文件" class="headerlink" title="4.设置hexoblog文件夹下的_config文件"></a>4.设置hexoblog文件夹下的_config文件</h3><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-number">01</span>找到<span class="hljs-meta"># Deployment</span><br><span class="hljs-number">02</span>配置<br><span class="hljs-symbol">type:</span> git<br><span class="hljs-symbol">repo:</span> https:<span class="hljs-comment">//github.com/codeMegan/codeMegan.github.io.git</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">branch:</span> master<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-输入账号-密码"><a href="#5-输入账号-密码" class="headerlink" title="5.输入账号&amp;密码"></a>5.输入账号&amp;密码</h3><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.email</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;lyjs0012@hotmail.com&quot;</span><br>git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.name</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;codeMegan&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-配置SSH"><a href="#6-配置SSH" class="headerlink" title="6.配置SSH"></a>6.配置SSH</h3><figure class="highlight mathematica"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs mathematica"><span class="hljs-number">01</span>生成密钥<br><span class="hljs-variable">ssh</span><span class="hljs-operator">-</span><span class="hljs-variable">keygen</span> <span class="hljs-operator">-</span><span class="hljs-variable">t</span> <span class="hljs-variable">rsa</span> <span class="hljs-operator">-</span><span class="hljs-built_in">C</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;lyjs0012@hotmail.com&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-number">02</span>在<span class="hljs-built_in">C</span>盘用户内找到密钥<br><span class="hljs-number">03</span>配置到<span class="hljs-variable">github</span><br>账号<span class="hljs-operator">--</span><span class="hljs-variable">setting</span><span class="hljs-operator">--</span><span class="hljs-variable">SSH</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7-部署到远端"><a href="#7-部署到远端" class="headerlink" title="7.部署到远端"></a>7.部署到远端</h3><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">hexo d</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="8-访问"><a href="#8-访问" class="headerlink" title="8.访问"></a>8.访问</h3><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-symbol">https:</span><span class="hljs-comment">//codemegan.github.io/</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="五、如何给个人博客更换主题"><a href="#五、如何给个人博客更换主题" class="headerlink" title="五、如何给个人博客更换主题"></a>五、如何给个人博客更换主题</h2><h3 id="1-下载主题并放置在themes文件夹下"><a href="#1-下载主题并放置在themes文件夹下" class="headerlink" title="1.下载主题并放置在themes文件夹下"></a>1.下载主题并放置在themes文件夹下</h3><h3 id="2-将根目录-config文件中的theme-landscape更改为theme-butterfly"><a href="#2-将根目录-config文件中的theme-landscape更改为theme-butterfly" class="headerlink" title="2.将根目录_config文件中的theme: landscape更改为theme: butterfly"></a>2.将根目录_config文件中的theme: landscape更改为theme: butterfly</h3><h3 id="3-将butterfly文件夹下的-config复制到根目录并重命名为-config-butterfly"><a href="#3-将butterfly文件夹下的-config复制到根目录并重命名为-config-butterfly" class="headerlink" title="3.将butterfly文件夹下的_config复制到根目录并重命名为_config.butterfly"></a>3.将butterfly文件夹下的_config复制到根目录并重命名为_config.butterfly</h3><h3 id="4-具体更改参考"><a href="#4-具体更改参考" class="headerlink" title="4.具体更改参考"></a>4.具体更改参考</h3><figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs avrasm"><span class="hljs-symbol">https:</span>//butterfly.js<span class="hljs-meta">.org</span>/posts/<span class="hljs-number">21</span>cfbf15/<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
